    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is a pristine 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in iconic Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. This chassis is mechanically impeccable, featuring factory-correct subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive service history addressing rod bearings. Zero aerodynamic or structural modifications; just pure, naturally aspirated performance with a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution and a taut, original suspension geometry.",
